snippet.title: Ninza - Early access trailer
snippet.description:
Ninza will be released on Steam Early Access beginning 2024.

Wishlist and play the demo during the Steam Neo Festival (starting 9th October):
https://store.steampowered.com/app/21...

Join our Discord for the latest infos :)
https://www.discord.gg/awR8MRx
